document.full_text: darius johnson-odom's 3-pointer with 27 seconds left snapped a tie and gave marquette a 66-62 win over syracuse on sunday night that put the golden eagles into the ncaa tournament's round of 16 for the first time in eight years.
document.title: no. 11 seed marquette tops 3rd-seeded syracuse
